These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, almond-milk
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | juice |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, analyst
1. the doctor is on the left or right of the analyst##3
2. the analyst is on the right of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Job   | doctor | analyst |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: cooking, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | cooking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, trance
1. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
2. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | trance | ambient |

 #################################

 
